snippet.title: Dragon Pinball - Xbox One / Windows 10 Gameplay
snippet.description:
NOTE: This is a Play Anywhere title on Xbox One, meaning that when you buy it once, you can play it on both Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S and Windows 10. The gameplay footage here is taken from the Windows 10 version.

Dragon Pinball is built from the Unity Asset Store and (somehow) made it on Switch, Xbox One, Steam and PlayStation 4. And while some can make something original out of the pre-made assets by adding your own custom-made ones, I am not 100% sure if this is the case.

Dragon Pinball (C) Super PowerUp Games S.L.
Xbox Store Page: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/dragon-pinball/9PBTH183Z1SK
